            <div><strong>Google로 계속하기</strong><small>3초 만에 회원가입</small></div>
            </a>

            <div class="start-divider">또는</div>

            <a href="/join-role" class="start-btn btn-email">
                <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"></rect><path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"></path></svg>
                <div><strong>이메일로 시작하기</strong><small>직접 회원가입</small></div>
            </a>

            <div class="login-link">이미 계정이 있으신가요? <a href="/login">로그인</a></div>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

{{> layout/footer}}